data.description: Come on out and show your pickiest buyers. Wow what a Gem this nicely kept home is. Fresh paint in and out. Roof only 7 months old, New Windows, AC and Hot water heater have recently been replaced. New flooring, new kitchen cabinets, countertops, Appliances, Backsplash and Refrigerator. Storage shed in back yard does convey. Plumbing is all PVC....no work needed on this home.
